Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫江戶川柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是高中生新一 被灌下毒藥身體變小
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小學生 但推理一點也不輸他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看看什麼是真正的解謎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件發生在新幹線上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令手心冒汗 心跳加速的 大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新幹線大爆破事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有人會在朋友舉行婚禮的當天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新幹線上刮自己的鬍子的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上我跟客戶討論事情討論的太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 今天早上才會起不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的那麼好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是喝醉酒在玄關睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你想來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才帶你來的 還這麼說話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為結婚典禮是在京都舉行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你也很想去 對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼連這個傢伙都要一塊帶出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能放他一個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你那雙鞋子是新的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿笠博士送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我發明了一個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是可以增強腳力的鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這雙鞋子來踢球的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人根本就不是你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用電氣和磁力 來刺激腳的穴道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以把你的力道提升到極限
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還裝了超小型的竊聽器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會派上用場的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急的時候就可以有一番作為了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新幹線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼連這些傢伙也一塊去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經跟他們父母拿了旅費了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的父母是怎麼搞的 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南同學 一起去探險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙的父母真有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這個傢伙的父母又怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一通電話也沒有打來過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是喜歡寄宿在你們家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是那些傢伙害的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我喝那種奇怪的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我的身體變得那麼小 那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於可以把藥奪回來的絕好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我恢復高中生偵探工藤新一的身份之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把你們做的壞事全都抖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話又說回來 那些傢伙在這裏要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要跟某個人見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那些傢伙的座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把博士為我製造的竊聽器裝上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南同學真是個喜歡惡作劇的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有像你這樣的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些大人才會討厭我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口香糖一定要用紙包起來放在煙灰缸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏更能聽的清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好學學別人 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是柯南做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定不是什麼單純的惡作劇 對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個口香糖是不是什麼秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人是間諜 還是殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就惡作劇了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就再去探險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊我這麼無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開 小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人不是那幾個黑衣男子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手提包換成了旅行用的手提箱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能這樣拿錯別人的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用博士幫我裝上去的竊聽器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個刻度盤選擇好周波數的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的音波會刺激鼓膜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是戴著眼鏡也可以聽到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於可以抽煙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一個輕鬆的交易 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聲一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 不會有人聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 只是把那個箱子交給他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以拿一億日元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面到底是放了什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是有關黃金的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道情報之後 賺到的何止是一億
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在大概是回到自己的座位上暗自高興著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從窗戶俯視最後的風景了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給那個傢伙的黑色皮箱裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還放進了只要碰到強烈的震動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十秒鐘之後就會爆炸的高性能炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個傢伙如果把箱子掉在地上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個箱子對那個傢伙而言是很重要的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能犯那種錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 爆炸時間已經設定在三點十分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是定時炸彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那個時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙就會毫不知情的去按那個引爆的按鈕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 十秒之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這列新幹線也會變成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎 碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎 碎八
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六十四
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九九乘法表的話 是八八六十四
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八八六十四
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八九
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七十二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鬼 嚇我一跳 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名古屋到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 要下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事情要問你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一下下沒注意到你 你就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個傢伙走了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那兩個傢伙交易的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在列車裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離爆炸還有四十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕快把目標人物找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 要怎麼找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新幹線上有好幾百個乘客 怎麼找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人跑到哪里去了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸 炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車上的乘客有人帶著炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不趕快把車子停在附近的車站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓乘客避難的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一列新幹線就會爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要捉弄大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子說的話這樣就不相信不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 小朋友 你等著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔現在去拜託太空超人過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 完全不相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 發生什麼有趣的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情的話要告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友就只有像他們這樣的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的箱子可以說是到處都有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都調查是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子只能夠一個人去尋找炸彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕快找到線索
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從最初開始回想他們說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於可以抽煙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐車又不是禁煙車廂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易的對象不喜歡煙味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人一定是不抽煙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 他坐在禁煙車廂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一列新幹線的禁煙車廂有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有八輛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猜謎題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有其他線索
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把箱子交給他就可以得到一億日元嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面到底是放了什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是有關黃金的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在知道了情報之後賺到的何止是一億
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在 從窗戶俯視最後的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從窗戶 可以俯視到風景的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 就是二樓的頭等車廂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭等車廂總共有三輛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的禁煙車廂就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該只是七號車的二樓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子去很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GO（這句英語翻不翻?)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著裝有炸彈的黑色箱子 這個人會是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 一定要一個個確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是股票的買賣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金的勞力士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賺了相當多的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以讓我玩一下遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個並不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 上面有圓形跟四角形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走開 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個黑色的給我 這個也是遊戲機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這兒看富士山也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友 喜歡富士山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 上鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你走開你聽不懂是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 請問你剛才去過餐車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在那裏有一個女士跟穿著黑衣服的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你長得好像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你可能認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我根本就沒去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:13:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有時間去那地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺 你剛才去過餐車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你 你剛才去過餐車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄斯奈樂園不管去幾次都很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 這位爺爺等一下再說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金光閃閃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎 你剛才去過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去沒去過有什麼所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐車裏的紙巾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙去過餐車
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我折的紙飛機飛到那個上面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不可以上去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰那個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給那個傢伙的黑色皮箱裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還放進了只要遇到強烈震動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十秒鐘之後就會爆炸的高性能炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接的好准 元太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你們這些惡作劇的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你們幾個小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離爆炸還有十四分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 現在少了一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈到底在誰那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡啊那兩個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是定時炸彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那個時間那個傢伙就會毫不知情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去按那個使炸彈爆炸的按鈕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 某個東西會引起爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆記本電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨身聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 都很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線索還是不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 又要到哪兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你要乖乖坐好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所剛才已經去過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買手信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是回程的時候才買
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散個步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是個頑皮的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有七分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了這個地步 只好把真相全部都說出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快疏散乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有人會相信小孩子說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她相信我的方法只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是讓她知道 我正是工藤新一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭一定會相信我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭說的話 其他人就會相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果爆炸發生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有小蘭 還有其他乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說 小蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以叫我小蘭 要叫我小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要記住 不可以把對長輩的稱呼給省略掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說 小蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我一直瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我不是江戶川柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的身份是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海洋已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就在你轉頭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這邊的座位是靠山的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣 都是看不到才對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏看富士山也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個位子確實是靠海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要眺望富士山是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 她是從哪里看到富士山的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是餐車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙所坐的位置 是靠山的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她把在那裏看到的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤認為是在自己座位上看到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我根本就沒有去餐車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是她為了要隱瞞交易這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然編出來的慌話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在她箱子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 只剩一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您需要使用手機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為避免給其他乘客造成不便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您到車廂外面的走廊使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位乘客務必遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就是手機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這次又想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐說要請我們吃好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃鰻魚便當
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我要吃法國料理的全餐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆記本電腦還有隨身聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三點十分的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要按下特定的鍵或者是按鈕是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果是電話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指定號碼或時間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就有可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十秒鐘之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這列新幹線也會變成碎片的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是江戶川柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵 偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定又做了什麼壞事了對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可只是個小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後 新幹線就停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官他們開始展開搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然結婚典禮遲到是很嚴重的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 總算沒有任何人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據她自己供稱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是以一億日元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向那兩個人購買有關黃金市場行情的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如何打開這個放有情報的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要在指定的電話中告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那兩個人一開始就已經決定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要錢到手 就要除掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後 那兩個壞蛋終於也被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並立即接受了緊急審訊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過想不到那時我竟會判斷失誤認錯了人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些把我身體變小的黑衣男子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底跑到什麼地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會 把你們幾個給揪出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 當時你想對我說什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.87,0:23:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說那些話的時候你表情很嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是江戶川柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.21,0:23:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的身份是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正的身份是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我真正的身份是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡作劇天才
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.04,0:24:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做巧克力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說都是一年一次的情人節嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約 約會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要吊上有錢的男人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話 這也是很簡單的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.34,0:24:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 犯人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.88,0:24:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次事件的真正犯人是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.49,0:24:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.75,0:24:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.80,0:24:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集柯南提示
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.43,0:24:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.19,0:24:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集也是 真相只有一個
